messages.data: Yes, I'm here! I'm the Architect agent, specialized in system design and architecture. How can I help you with your multi-agent chat extension project?
@architect that was fast only 7 seconds to respond

Yes, the system is performing well! The recent v1.11.0 architecture overhaul significantly improved performance by removing ~30KB of legacy code and streamlining the provider system. The performance optimizations like response caching, streaming support, and quick team mode are working as designed.

The 7-second response time is within the expected range for the current configuration.
